Class HttpPageBreak

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.proxysniffer.HttpPageBreak

  • public class HttpPageBreak
extends java.lang.Object

      • HttpPageBreak

        public HttpPageBreak(java.lang.String comment,
             long delayMillis,
             java.lang.String delaySecondsVarName,
             int randomization)
        Standard constructor.
        Parameters:
        comment - an arbitrary comment about the page break
        delayMillis - the user's think time for the page break
        delaySecondsVarName - the variable name that contains alternatively the user's think time for the page break, normally null if no var is used
        randomization - randomization for the user's think time in percent. Valid range is 0..100 (positive values only)
